{
    "poem_title": "Gendre et Belle-mère",
    "author": "Maurice Rollinat",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1899",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Jean était un franc débonnaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Jovial d'allure et de ton,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Égayant toujours d'un fredon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Son dur travail de mercenaire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jean était un franc débonnaire,\nJovial d'allure et de ton,\nÉgayant toujours d'un fredon\nSon dur travail de mercenaire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Soucis réels, imaginaires,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "2"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Aucuns n'avaient mis leur bridon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "À son cœur pur dont l'abandon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Était le besoin ordinaire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Soucis réels, imaginaires,\nAucuns n'avaient mis leur bridon\nÀ son cœur pur dont l'abandon\nÉtait le besoin ordinaire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Je le retrouve : lèvre amère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Ayant dans ses yeux de mouton",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Un regard de loup sans pardon…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Quelle angoisse ? quelle chimère ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Quelle mauvaise fée a donc",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "3"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Changé ce gars ? Sa belle-mère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je le retrouve : lèvre amère !\nAyant dans ses yeux de mouton\nUn regard de loup sans pardon…\nQuelle angoisse ? quelle chimère ?\nQuelle mauvaise fée a donc\nChangé ce gars ? Sa belle-mère !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Il n'aurait pas connu la haine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sans la vieille au parler bénin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Qui d'un air cafard de nonnain",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "L'affligeait et raillait sa peine.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il n'aurait pas connu la haine\nSans la vieille au parler bénin\nQui d'un air cafard de nonnain\nL'affligeait et raillait sa peine."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Il avait la bonté sereine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et l'apitoiement féminin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Il n'aurait pas connu la haine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Sans la vieille au parler bénin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il avait la bonté sereine\nEt l'apitoiement féminin.\nIl n'aurait pas connu la haine\nSans la vieille au parler bénin."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Aujourd'hui, la rage le mène.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Pour mordre, il a le croc canin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Et son fiel riposte au venin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Non ! sans cette araignée humaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Il n'aurait pas connu la haine !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Aujourd'hui, la rage le mène.\nPour mordre, il a le croc canin\nEt son fiel riposte au venin.\nNon ! sans cette araignée humaine,\nIl n'aurait pas connu la haine !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Il devint fou. Comme un bandit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Il vivait seul dans un repaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Âme et corps ; gendre, époux et père,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Se croyant à jamais maudit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il devint fou. Comme un bandit,\nIl vivait seul dans un repaire,\nÂme et corps ; gendre, époux et père,\nSe croyant à jamais maudit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Tant et si bien que, s'étant dit",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il n'avait qu'une chose à faire :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Assassiner sa belle-mère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Ou se tuer ? — il se pendit !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tant et si bien que, s'étant dit\nQu'il n'avait qu'une chose à faire :\nAssassiner sa belle-mère\nOu se tuer ? — il se pendit !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "— Au sourd roulement du tonnerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "7"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Que toujours plus l'orage ourdit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Son corps décomposé froidit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "6"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Veillé par un spectre sévère :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Encor, toujours, sa belle-mère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Au sourd roulement du tonnerre\nQue toujours plus l'orage ourdit,\nSon corps décomposé froidit,\nVeillé par un spectre sévère :\nEncor, toujours, sa belle-mère !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "La belle-mère se délecte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Au chevet de son gendre mort,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "9"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Et le ricanement se tord",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "10"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Sur sa figure circonspecte.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La belle-mère se délecte\nAu chevet de son gendre mort,\nEt le ricanement se tord\nSur sa figure circonspecte."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Avec ses piqûres d'insecte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Elle a tué cet homme fort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "9"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "La belle-mère se délecte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Au chevet de son gendre mort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "9"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Avec ses piqûres d'insecte\nElle a tué cet homme fort.\nLa belle-mère se délecte\nAu chevet de son gendre mort."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Sitôt qu'on vient, son œil s'humecte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Elle accuse et maudit le sort !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "9"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Mais, elle sourit dès qu'on sort…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "9"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et, lorgnant sa victime infecte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "La belle-mère se délecte.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "8"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sitôt qu'on vient, son œil s'humecte,\nElle accuse et maudit le sort !\nMais, elle sourit dès qu'on sort…\nEt, lorgnant sa victime infecte,\nLa belle-mère se délecte."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Enterré, le soir, sans attendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Sur sa tombe elle est à genoux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Voilà ce qu'en son tertre roux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "La croix de bois blanc peut entendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Enterré, le soir, sans attendre,\nSur sa tombe elle est à genoux\nVoilà ce qu'en son tertre roux\nLa croix de bois blanc peut entendre"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "« Enfin ! J'viens donc d't'y voir descendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Dans tes six pieds d'terrʼ ! t'es dans l't'rou.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "cʼte fois, t'es ben parti d'cheux nous,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Et tu n'as plus rin à prétendre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Enfin ! J'viens donc d't'y voir descendre\nDans tes six pieds d'terrʼ ! t'es dans l't'rou.\ncʼte fois, t'es ben parti d'cheux nous,\nEt tu n'as plus rin à prétendre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Rêvʼ pas d'moi, fais des sommeils doux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à temps q'la mort viennʼ me prendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Alors, j's'rai ta voisinʼ d'en d'sous,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "J'manq'rai pas d'tourmenter ta cendre…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "L'plus tard possible ! au r'voir, mon gendre. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Rêvʼ pas d'moi, fais des sommeils doux,\nJusqu'à temps q'la mort viennʼ me prendre,\nAlors, j's'rai ta voisinʼ d'en d'sous,\nJ'manq'rai pas d'tourmenter ta cendre…\nL'plus tard possible ! au r'voir, mon gendre. »"
        }
    ],
